lass=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">myblog</span>.<span class=\"cm-property\" style=\"color:#000000;\">wsgi</span></span> <span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">home</span>            = <span class=\"cm-operator\" style=\"color:#981A1A;\">/</span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">root</span><span class=\"cm-operator\" style=\"color:#981A1A;\">/</span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">Envs</span><span class=\"cm-operator\" style=\"color:#981A1A;\">/</span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">myblog</span></span> <span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">master</span>          = <span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">true</span></span> <span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">processes</span>       = <span class=\"cm-number\" style=\"color:#116644;\">1</span></span> <span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">socket</span>          = <span class=\"cm-number\" style=\"color:#116644;\">0.0.0.0</span>:<span class=\"cm-number\" style=\"color:#116644;\">9000</span>    </span> <span><span class=\"cm-comment\" style=\"color:#AA5500;\">#http            = 0.0.0.0:9000</span></span> <span><span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">vacuum</span>          = <span class=\"cm-variable\" style=\"color:#000000;\">true</span></span></pre>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\'color:#333333;font-family:\"Open Sans\", \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;\'>\n<span class=\"md-plain\">过指定uwsgi.ini配置文件把django跑起来(myblog的ini文件在myblog/myblog/)</span>\n</p>\n<pre class=\"md-fences md-end-block ty-contain-cm modeLoaded\"><span>uwsgi uwsgi.ini</span></pre>\n<p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\'color:#333333;font-family:\"Open Sans\", \"Clear Sans\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;\'>\n<span class=\"md-plain\">只使用uwsgi.ini 启动django项目的时候，前端使用线上服务器加端口访问的时候，前端会显示”该